Business Insights 360 Power BI Project Overview

Purpose:
This Power BI dashboard helps AtliQ Hardware make informed decisions by providing insights into Finance, Sales, Marketing, and Supply Chain.

Key Insights:

Finance View:

Tracks important KPIs like Net Sales, Gross Margin %, and Net Profit %.
Includes a detailed Profit & Loss Statement with year-over-year growth.
Sales View:

Analyzes customer performance based on Net Sales and Gross Margin.
Marketing View:

Shows how different segments perform and their Net Profit.
Supply Chain View:

Compares Actual Sales with Forecasted Sales to check accuracy.
Executive View:

Reviews yearly trends in Revenue, Gross Margin %, Net Profit %, and Market Share %.
Lists the Top 5 Customers and Products by Revenue.
